%matplotlib inline

from pymote import NetworkGenerator
from pymote import write_pickle, read_pickle
from pymote.environment import Environment2D

net_gen = NetworkGenerator(30, comm_range=500)
net = net_gen.generate_random_network()
net.environment = Environment2D(shape=(800,800))
net.show()

net.algorithms = (MegaMerger, )

write_pickle(net, "MegaMerger.npc.gz")

def count_districts_in_city_name(name):
    replacables = [("[", ""), ("]", ""), ("A", "_"), ("F", "_")]
    for replacable in replacables:
        name = name.replace(*replacable)
    ids = set()
    for node_id in name.split("_"):
        ids.add(int(node_id))
    return len(ids)

def print_result(node):
    print("Node id: {}, Level: {}, Downtown id: {}, Neighbours in MST: {}".format(
        node.id, node.memory["level"], node.memory["downtown_id"], node.memory["neighbours_in_city"]
    ))

city_name = net.nodes()[0].memory["city_name"]
print("New city name: {}".format(city_name))
print("Number of districts in new city: {}".format(count_districts_in_city_name(city_name)))

for node in net.nodes():
    print_result(node)
